## Success Criteria for the Pilot

The pilot will be considered successful if we can demonstrate that:

* Teams can get onboarded without excessive friction
* Backlog generation is useful enough for real team workflows
* Jira updates better reflect engineering execution
* Participants can run a real business use case end to end
* Feedback is concrete enough to improve the workflow for broader rollout

## Phase 2 Direction

After Sprint 2, the next phase is expected to expand more broadly across CORE.

That phase is expected to:

* incorporate pilot feedback
* refine setup and workflow documentation
* improve any issues found during the pilot
* expand usage across a broader audience

